      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MY CUPCAKE (7) has a strong record here with six wins and four placings from 15 starts. Missed the frame latest (22.36) when fourth over 388m at Gosford in a NG. Has the ability and should feature. ZIPPING DELORIS (8) is an honest type in the frame at 12 of 30 starts including 10 wins, the latest scoring (17.69) over 300m at Taree Super Track. Performs well off this draw. Looks suited and expected to run well. PAPER SHREDDER (2) settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 5th (22.71) at Gosford. Form here at the trip sound including six wins. Should be thereabouts. HOUSIE BOB (1) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
